<edu>But most of the drug money is kept in investments and in financial institutions outside Colombia . <s></edu>
<edu>In fact , the cooperation of those financial institutions is essential to the success of the drug battle . <s></edu>
<edu>What is of much more importance to the Colombian economy than the supposed benefits of laundered drug money is higher prices for Colombia 's legitimate products . <s></edu>
<edu>The price of coffee has gone down almost 45 % since the beginning of the year , to the lowest level <s></edu>
<edu>( after inflation ) <s></edu>
