<edu>The 27-year-old coffee cartel had to be formally dissolved this summer . <s></edu>
<edu>As a result , Colombia will earn $ 500 million less from its coffee this year than last . <s></edu>
<edu>Our coffee growers face reductions in their income , <s></edu>
<edu>and this tempts them to contemplate substituting coca crops for coffee . <s></edu>
<edu>U.S. interests occasionally try to impose barriers to the import of another important Colombian export <s></edu>
<edu>-- cut flowers -- <s></edu>
<edu>into the American market . <s></edu>
<edu>A just price and an open market <s></edu>
<edu>for what Colombian produces and exports <s></edu>
<edu>should be the policy of the U.S. <s></edu>
